      <title>我的个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/02/wo-de-ge-ren-bo-ke/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/02/wo-de-ge-ren-bo-ke/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="为什么要搭建自己的个人博客"><a href="#为什么要搭建自己的个人博客" class="headerlink" title="为什么要搭建自己的个人博客?"></a><strong>为什么要搭建自己的个人博客?</strong></h2><blockquote><p>1、功利一点，为了好找工作！</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>2、从不喜欢做笔记的我，希望也开始用博客作为自己的学习记录</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>3、坚持写博客。有句话叫贵在坚持，去年也搭建过自己的个人博客，但是由于自己后来不小心把数据库给删了（我真是猪），然后就没有在写博客了。</p></blockquote><h5 id="最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello-World！”，哈哈哈。"><a href="#最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello-World！”，哈哈哈。" class="headerlink" title="最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello World！”，哈哈哈。"></a>最后，先来走一遍程序，来几个“Hello World！”，哈哈哈。</h5><pre class="line-numbers language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">HelloWorld</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Hello ,我的博客！"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><pre class="line-numbers language-c++"><code class="language-c++">#include<iostream>using namespace std;int main(){    cout<<"Hello ,我的个人博客"<< endl;    return 0;}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><hr><pre class="line-numbers language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Hello ,我的个人博客！"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
